Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:10.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去趟防火水槽吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又来了  那可不是女高中生该去的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上要顺便去趟大工咖啡店吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.03,0:00:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里整个的运作系统都有了很大的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.52,0:00:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对麻衣来说也许有点难懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把那里的各种各样的事情都教给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是非对称
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:53.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(375,340)\fs20}Asymmetry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.98,0:00:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  虽然你说的没错  但这已经是很强烈的不对称了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经超越了漂亮的界限了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.90,0:01:07.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探究得太深了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  这好像已经完全不知道意思了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天也是站在麻衣这边的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:04.46,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,300)\fad(400,400)}日\N常\N之\N68
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的菜色  要怎么配好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.66,0:03:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葱好像很便宜  做葱料理怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是博士讨厌吃葱的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你看  我抓住了一只乌鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你都做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做很危险的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被啄伤的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知在何时围巾就突然不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是乌鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后还请多多赏脸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好它是一只有礼貌的乌鸦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是乌鸦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到您的称赞是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它喝草莓牛奶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果会喝的话还真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚊子…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.21,0:04:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还帮我们消灭蚊虫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  这是我应该做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是乌鸦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  阪本先生  你的围巾上哪儿去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有围巾的话  就听不懂它在说什么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来试着听听看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像它很想要我的围巾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的围巾吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  难道你把阪本先生的围巾给乌鸦戴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样的话阪本先生就太可怜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  我再去做一条
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是饼干1号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和围巾没有半毛钱关系！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问博士  饼干1号有着什么样的机能呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鸦问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会放出火箭拳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要来一发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.71,0:06:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博…博士  差不多该给阪本先生围…围巾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还有左手在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备…发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把这些家伙全部杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.11,0:06:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  今天真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我好像玩笑开过头了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把这个围巾还给阪本先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很短暂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够说人类的语言我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:06:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鸦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走  乌鸦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有机会的话  我们再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家请多多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See  you  again！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鸦～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然戴着飞走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办不到的啦  课长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.98,0:07:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法信任我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是那么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是完全信任课长的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.58,0:07:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那么就请助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  疼疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
