Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:19.00,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(290,320)\fad(40,400)}体\N育\N馆\N后\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在体育馆后面挖好了黏着剂陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就用这封信把她约出来骗到陷阱里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要抓住你  东云名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.50,0:01:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:20.45,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,300)\fad(400,400)}日\N常\N之\N70
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:20.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到樱井诚居然是樱井老师的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.81,0:13:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我得想办法问到樱井老师的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:32.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会踢围棋足球吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  樱井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你有在交往中的男朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No  future！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么总是这样  我这种男人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这种男人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  没有倒是没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有倒是没有啦…  没有倒是没有啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长…长…长出来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长出来啦！  我发达了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:06.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的你就视而不见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你在踢围棋足球吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有在踢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道老师你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢我们家姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是作为围棋足球部的学长在和你说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.78,0:14:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  你会踢围棋足球吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在高中可是MVP！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  其实现在我们的围棋足球部还没有顾问老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您能来当顾问老师的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于我姐姐的事我会全力协助的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我才没有喜欢她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您不来当顾问老师的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去散布您喜欢我姐姐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.09,0:14:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要来当顾问老师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是不来当呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…  当顾问很麻烦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你这威胁者！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…追上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中之条君在体育馆后面被埋住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能尽快来一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  高崎老师他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.49,0:15:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中之条他…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有被埋住！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.86,0:15:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  他只是一杆进洞了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的头发都被拔掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我画上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:45.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我试试！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:52.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起被埋  去管教暴露他人隐私的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是作为教育者…怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样才是教育者啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高崎老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我等着您来当顾问老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可真懂事儿～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安中  要走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点赶过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才是教师该做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.41,0:16:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是顺势而行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剃掉别人头发终究还是不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:35.87,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,320)\fad(40,400)}体\N育\N馆\N后\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正他也不知道是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:42.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.84,0:16:43.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}啊咧  啊咧咧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里  这里是哪里  好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么  动不了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.82,0:16:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  怎么了怎么了怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.33,0:16:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水  水  鲨鱼鲨鱼  啪咔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲨鱼鲨鱼  啪库
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:11.82,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,380)\fs30}琪琪其实是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:29.64,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,320)\fad(400,400)\bord10\shad0\be60\3c&HFFFFFF&}体\N育\N馆\N后\N3
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:31.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:34.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.99,0:17:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.85,0:17:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:45.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真是的  好危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.72,0:17:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发被…
Dialogue: 0,-0:00:00.50,-0:00:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:06.96,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(80,300)\fad(400,400)}日\N常\N之\N71
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我绝对不会吐槽的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底  都是麻衣的不对嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.26,0:18:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像机械一样装傻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次每次都惹我吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  就是装傻与吐槽的死循环了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  本该是比花更加娇艳的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可却无法像普通的女高中生那样交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天开始我绝对不会吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的意志可是比钻石还要坚硬！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  麻衣早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双重眼镜！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强烈啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天好强烈啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏今天那么强烈啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:00.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不会认输！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我  因为我们已经改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}印尼语早安的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:10.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  现在才是让少女谈话之花绽放的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.93,0:19:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  我说  麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上的「肌肉镇魂歌」看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…  哪哪哪哪边！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.96,0:19:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜  眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是这种快节奏的装傻！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她简直就像是在等着我吐槽一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不能吐槽  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是陷阱！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  水上  你不是已经戴了两副眼镜了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田中这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的吐槽…  把只能由我来的无上的吐槽给…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对  不是我的  那并不是只属于我的吐槽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:20:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  今天的第一节课是国语吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的哦  这么说来教理科的中村好像昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  她没事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  今天的第一节课是国语吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧  这个你刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好危险！  这女孩居然说两遍同样的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是前途堪忧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.52,0:20:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女孩真是前途堪忧啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  喊口令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}麻衣故意把「ちゃくせき」说成「ちゃくせこ」。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始上课
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:36.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说坐吓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吓是什么东西啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全班都假装无视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么有人愿意来读吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.11,0:20:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻…麻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  水上你来读
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:03.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}山安静而阴暗  村落闪烁着点点灯光…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而…而且
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.10,0:21:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这样读就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这样读就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都背下来了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然吐槽真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.80,0:21:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.29,0:22:10.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发出这么大的声音真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去走廊罚站
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  这样就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是麻衣的生存之道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我从今天早上开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就戴着隐形眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴眼镜压根就没意义嘛
